[
    {
        "text": "Meanwhile in Lanka,",
        "start": 5.82,
        "duration": 1.84
    },
    {
        "text": "Ravana refused to listen",
        "start": 8.26,
        "duration": 1.68
    },
    {
        "text": "to the wise counsel",
        "start": 10.02,
        "duration": 1.26
    },
    {
        "text": "of his younger brother, Vibheeshana.",
        "start": 11.28,
        "duration": 1.9
    },
    {
        "text": "Vibheeshana knew that if war broke out,",
        "start": 13.74,
        "duration": 2.84
    },
    {
        "text": "it would mean the end of the demon race.",
        "start": 16.74,
        "duration": 2.76
    },
    {
        "text": "But Vibheeshana's words",
        "start": 20.64,
        "duration": 1.64
    },
    {
        "text": "hurt Ravana's ego",
        "start": 22.28,
        "duration": 1.62
    },
    {
        "text": "and he accused Vibheeshana",
        "start": 24.14,
        "duration": 1.76
    },
    {
        "text": "of being a traitor.",
        "start": 25.96,
        "duration": 1.18
    },
    {
        "text": "Hurt by this,",
        "start": 36.52,
        "duration": 1.18
    },
    {
        "text": "Vibheeshana went to Rama,",
        "start": 38.02,
        "duration": 1.7
    },
    {
        "text": "and sort refuge under him",
        "start": 40.0,
        "duration": 1.76
    },
    {
        "text": "Sri Rama accepted Vibheeshana.",
        "start": 48.14,
        "duration": 2.46
    },
    {
        "text": "And promised him that,",
        "start": 50.96,
        "duration": 1.4
    },
    {
        "text": "upon Ravana's death",
        "start": 52.38,
        "duration": 1.54
    },
    {
        "text": "he would be the king of Lanka.",
        "start": 54.32,
        "duration": 1.94
    },
    {
        "text": "Vibheeshana asks Rama to pray to the Sea God",
        "start": 97.02,
        "duration": 3.62
    },
    {
        "text": "to build a bridge across the ocean.",
        "start": 100.84,
        "duration": 2.14
    },
    {
        "text": "Rama prays for a whole day",
        "start": 103.38,
        "duration": 2.38
    },
    {
        "text": "but there is no response from the Sea god.",
        "start": 106.18,
        "duration": 2.72
    },
    {
        "text": "Rama gets dejected",
        "start": 109.54,
        "duration": 1.54
    },
    {
        "text": "he gets angry,",
        "start": 111.56,
        "duration": 1.04
    },
    {
        "text": "and gets ready to attack the ocean.",
        "start": 112.84,
        "duration": 2.26
    },
    {
        "text": "Then suddenly the sea God emerges,",
        "start": 115.62,
        "duration": 2.44
    },
    {
        "text": "and asks Rama to build the bridge over the sea.",
        "start": 118.18,
        "duration": 3.12
    },
    {
        "text": "The vanaras build the bridge",
        "start": 124.5,
        "duration": 1.74
    },
    {
        "text": "across the sea",
        "start": 126.26,
        "duration": 0.96
    },
    {
        "text": "by placing stones, trees and sand.",
        "start": 127.56,
        "duration": 2.8
    },
    {
        "text": "The bridge was ready in five days.",
        "start": 212.1,
        "duration": 2.6
    },
    {
        "text": "Cheering with excitement,",
        "start": 220.96,
        "duration": 1.84
    },
    {
        "text": "the vanara army crossed the sea,",
        "start": 222.98,
        "duration": 2.44
    },
    {
        "text": "and reached Lanka.",
        "start": 225.82,
        "duration": 1.54
    },
    {
        "text": "Ravana sent many more demons,",
        "start": 237.88,
        "duration": 2.44
    },
    {
        "text": "who were very good at warfare.",
        "start": 240.58,
        "duration": 1.66
    },
    {
        "text": "A fierce battle broke out,",
        "start": 243.86,
        "duration": 1.68
    },
    {
        "text": "between the vanaras and the demons.",
        "start": 245.7,
        "duration": 2.3
    },
    {
        "text": "Each one of the vanaras fought bravely,",
        "start": 251.46,
        "duration": 2.76
    },
    {
        "text": "and injured or killed  many demons.",
        "start": 254.72,
        "duration": 2.4
    },
    {
        "text": "The demons fought equally well.",
        "start": 258.06,
        "duration": 2.38
    },
    {
        "text": "Ravana felt very humiliated.",
        "start": 285.06,
        "duration": 2.4
    },
    {
        "text": "Ravana now woke up the sleeping giant Kumbakarna.",
        "start": 288.06,
        "duration": 3.66
    },
    {
        "text": "He was Ravana's brother.",
        "start": 295.4,
        "duration": 1.66
    },
    {
        "text": "He ate for six months",
        "start": 297.86,
        "duration": 1.92
    },
    {
        "text": "and slept for six months.",
        "start": 299.9,
        "duration": 1.72
    },
    {
        "text": "Ravana knew that only he could save",
        "start": 302.18,
        "duration": 2.74
    },
    {
        "text": "Lanka from ruin.",
        "start": 304.94,
        "duration": 1.1
    },
    {
        "text": "When Kumbakarna came to know",
        "start": 317.56,
        "duration": 1.9
    },
    {
        "text": "that he was woken up",
        "start": 319.56,
        "duration": 1.12
    },
    {
        "text": "because of the war",
        "start": 320.74,
        "duration": 1.3
    },
    {
        "text": "he walked towards the battlefield.",
        "start": 322.76,
        "duration": 2.3
    },
    {
        "text": "He was very huge and massive,",
        "start": 329.38,
        "duration": 2.64
    },
    {
        "text": "the vanaras were terrified of his size and form",
        "start": 332.72,
        "duration": 3.38
    },
    {
        "text": "They were no match for him",
        "start": 336.66,
        "duration": 2.04
    },
    {
        "text": "After seeing the panic in the vanaras,",
        "start": 344.1,
        "duration": 2.56
    },
    {
        "text": "Rama rose to face Kumbakarna.",
        "start": 346.98,
        "duration": 2.46
    },
    {
        "text": "A fierce battle was waged.",
        "start": 350.3,
        "duration": 2.3
    },
    {
        "text": "Rama used one of his powerul weapons",
        "start": 353.12,
        "duration": 2.82
    },
    {
        "text": "and chopped Kumbakarna's arms and legs,",
        "start": 356.14,
        "duration": 2.74
    },
    {
        "text": "Kumabakarna died.",
        "start": 359.5,
        "duration": 1.36
    },
    {
        "text": "The vanaras felt very happy at the success.",
        "start": 361.8,
        "duration": 3.36
    }
]